node.text:
Baby axolotls from @axolotlplanet 🤯 Would you keep one of these as a pet? They are little anomalies of nature with an incredible ability to regenerate limbs, parts of their organs, and some of their spinal cord! 🥴 Not to mention, they’re 1,000X more resistant to cancer than we are! 🧬

🔔 Turn on our post notifications to be the first to see some of the most amazing aquatic life on Instagram! 😍⁠
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⁠⁠ ⠀
